Michael O'Halleran
Executive Chairman, Aon Benfield
Senior Executive Vice President, Aon plc

Michael D. O'Halleran is Executive Chairman of Aon Benfield and Senior Executive Vice President of Aon plc. Mike was appointed to lead Aon's reinsurance division at its inception in 1987. Previously, he held several senior operating positions at Aon. Before joining the Firm, he was a senior executive with well-known companies within the insurance industry, including Wausau Insurance Companies, General Reinsurance and Alexander Re. Mike has more than 33 years of experience in the insurance and reinsurance industries. He is also a member of the Economic Club of Chicago and the World Presidents Organization.























